text:
Good Afternoon,

Hope your trip back was great!

We spoke last time, that we might have a call on Sunday(today). 
Unfortunately, I have not done anything yet, due to work. I am very sorry. 

Would you mind if we could have a call after Christmas? By then, I will make sure to be done with UV's. 

Unless, you would like to talk about something else!  Then it is perfectly fine, haha :D

Hey Silvija! That’s no problem! There’s no real rush at all! Just the sooner you’re confident with it really!
We can wait will after Christmas, more things to discuss and give feedback on, especially this bow sculpt! :)

Thank you very much! I will make sure to do my tasks well, haha! :D 

Have a lovely Christmas with your family! :christmas_tree::relaxed::tada::fireworks:
